Thank you for choosing to take part in the survey!

In the survey, you will be asked 12 questions regarding your interracial relationship. The purpose of the survey is to assess how interracial relationships differ from intraracial ones. 
All data is anonymous and confidential and you may choose to opt out of the survey at any point.
